def inverse_slice(items, a, b):
    return items[:a] + items[b:]

def inverse_slice(items, a, b):
  return [v for i,v in enumerate(items) if i < a or i >= b]

def inverse_slice(items, a, b):
    return list(i for i in items if i not in items[a:b])

def inverse_slice(items, a, b):
    splice1 = items[:a]
    splice2 = items[b:]
    return splice1 + splice2

def inverse_slice(items, a, b):
    inv_list=items[0:a]
    inv_list.extend(items[b:])
    return inv_list
